                <h1>How an uncredited German producer’s free loops are powering platinum rap hits</h1>
                <h2 class="deck">The royalty-free instrumental loops Minor2Go posts on Looperman have been used in hit songs by Drake, Polo G, Gunna, Lil Tjay, YoungBoy Never Broke Again, and more. </h2>

            </div>

          </div>

          
          <div class="credits gutter_left triple_gutter_right">
              <div class="author">
    <span>
      By <span class="credit_name"><a href="/contributor/ben-dandridge-lemco">Ben Dandridge-Lemco</a></span>
  </div>


<div class="posted">
  <div>
    September 20, 2019
  </div>
</div>

          </div>

